===   SETUP INSTRUCTIONS   ===

1. Build the bundle by issuing:
   - bundle install

2. In the webserver public directory create symbolic links to:
   - /photickle/public/       [Main Site]
   - /photickle/coverage/     [Unit Tests]

   eg. 'ln -s ../photickle/public/ public' (access with http(s)://webserver.url/photickle/)

3. Restart the server by issuing:
   - 'touch /photickle/tmp/restart.txt'

.
